# Keep Claude Code's file tooling out of giant non-source trees.
# Without this, Claude walks ~337k files / 5GB+ and inflates its single Node heap → OOM crashes.
# (System has plenty of RAM; the limit is V8's per-process heap.) Diagnosis: 2026-06-02.

# Vendored runtimes, agent state, caches — 5GB / ~182k files, never source-of-truth
.project-manager/hermes/
.project-manager/openclaw/
.project-manager/vendor/
vendor/

# Python virtualenvs (large discovery-cache JSON blobs live here)
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/site-packages/

# Build / dependency output
node_modules/
out/
src-tauri/target/
target/
.next/

# Generated config backups
.project-manager/config.before-*.json
.project-manager/config.generated-*.backup.json
